An update as just been released, including a few changes to Counter-Strike and minor changes to the other Steam games<br/><br/>Counter-Strike dedicated server admins please note that this update requires your servers to restart. This can be done normally via the HLDS update tool, or the dedicated server update can be downloaded directly from <a href="/?area=dedicated_server">this page</a>. Also, if you run Metamod, you must <a href="http://www.metamod.org">download the new version</a> or your server will crash.<br/><br/><ul style="padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><b>COUNTER-STRIKE CHANGES:</b><br/><li>Improved damage and accuracy of sg550 and g3sg1 sniper rifles</li><br/><li>Added small shadow underneath player</li><br/><li>Added autobuy and rebuy functionality to buy menus</li><br/><br/><b>ALL GAMES:</b><br/><li>Added extra progress indicators for downloading &amp; initializing VAC security modules</li><br/><li>Removed 'cmd dlfile' console command from being accessed directly from the console</li><br/><li>Fixed servers not being in world list if they specified a region on startup</li><br/></ul><br/></p>
